sources.styles\\navbar.sass:
.navigation
    width: 100%
    z-index: 101
    
    .container 
        display: flex
        justify-content: space-between

    &__links 
        list-style-type: none
        padding: 0
        display: none
        align-self: center

        a
            text-decoration: none
            margin-left: 2rem

            &:hover
                color: $primaryBlue
                text-decoration: underline

        li:first-of-type a 
            font-weight: 500
            color: $primaryBlue

    &__author
        align-self: center
        color: $primaryBlue

    &__socials 
        display: flex
        align-items: center

        img 
            width: 22px
            height: 22px
            cursor: pointer
            
        a:first-of-type img
            width: 28px
            height: 28px
            
    @include useMinWidth(750px)
        position: sticky
        top: 0
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .97)

        &__links
            display: flex
        
        &__author
            display: none
sources.styles\\presentation.sass:
.presentation
    display: grid
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr
    grid-template-rows: 3fr 2fr 1fr
    grid-template-areas: 'header decoration' 'desc desc' 'actions actions'
    margin-bottom: 5rem

    &__btn 
        border-radius: 4px
        width: 130px
        height: 34px
        text-align: center
        outline: none
        cursor: pointer
        
        &--primary
            background: $primaryBlue
            color: white
            border: none

        &--secendary 
            background: white
            border: 1px solid $primaryBlue
            color: $primaryBlue

    &__author
        display: none
        grid-area: author
        align-self: center
        text-align: right
        color: $primaryBlue

    &__header
        grid-area: header
            
    &__desc
        grid-area: desc
        color: #685E5E
                
    &__big-img
        grid-area: big-img
        display: none

    &__actions
        grid-area: actions
        text-align: center
        display: flex

        button:nth-of-type(2)
            margin-left: spacing(1) 
    
    @include useMinWidth(750px)
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 
        grid-template-rows: 1fr 2fr 2fr
        grid-template-areas: 'author .' 'header big-img' 'desc big-img' 'actions .'

        &__big-img 
            display: inline
            width: 100%

        &__actions
            text-align: left

        &__author
            display: block
            text-align: left
            margin-bottom: 0
            align-self: end

    @include useMinWidth(850px)
        grid-template-columns: 100px 2fr .5fr 2fr
        grid-template-rows: 1.5fr 2fr 1fr 1.5fr
        grid-template-areas: 'decoration author . .' 'decoration header . big-img' 'decoration desc . big-img' 'decoration actions . .'

        &__header
            font-size: 2.5rem
        
        &__desc
            margin-top: 0
sources.styles\\decoration.sass:
$decoration-rect-size: 14px
$decoration-rect-rotate: rotate(45deg)
$decoration-rect-color:#6C63FF

.decoration
   grid-area: decoration
   position: relative

   span:first-of-type
      top: 40%
      left: 20px

   span:nth-of-type(2)
      top: 10%
      left: 30px
      transform: rotate(180deg)

   &__rect
      width: $decoration-rect-size
      height: $decoration-rect-size
      background: white
      border: 1px solid $decoration-rect-color
      transform: $decoration-rect-rotate
      position: absolute

      &::after
         content: ''
         width: $decoration-rect-size
         height: $decoration-rect-size
         position: absolute
         background: $decoration-rect-color
         right: 4px
         top: 2px

   @include useMinWidth(750px)
      & 
         display: none

   @include useMinWidth(850px)
      & 
         display: block

      // span:first-of-type
      //    top: 40%
      //    left: 20px

      span:nth-of-type(2)
         top: 18%
sources.styles\\carousel.sass:
.carlousel
   width: 100%
   background: transparent
   margin-bottom: 20px
   display: flex
   overflow: scroll
   cursor: grab
   user-select: none
   overflow-y: hidden

   &::-webkit-scrollbar 
      width: 40px
      height: spacing(1)

   &::-webkit-scrollbar-track 
      box-shadow: none
      border-radius: 10px

   &::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb 
      background: $primaryBlue
      border-radius: 10px

   &::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover 
      background: $primaryBlue

   &__box
      min-width: 270px
      margin: 20px
      position: relative
      height: 230px

      &__overlay *
         color: white
      
      img
         width: 100%
         z-index: -1
         user-select: text

      &__overlay
         background: rgba(97, 74, 237, 0.82)
         position: absolute
         width: 100%
         bottom: 0
         padding: 1rem .5rem .5rem 1rem
         padding-top: 0

         h
            margin-top: 0

         p  
            display: -webkit-box
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical
            overflow: hidden
            font-size: 14px

   @include useMinWidth(750px)
      &
         width: 80%
         margin: 0 auto
sources.styles\\projects.sass:
.projects
   background: $backgroundGray
   padding: 5rem 0

   &__desc
      text-align: center

   &__header
      display: inline
      position: relative

      &::after
         content: ''
         background: $primaryBlue
         height: 2px
         display: block
         position: absolute
         width: 70%
         left: 50%
         transform: translate(-50%, 28px)

   &__body
      margin-top: 44px + 28px
      color: $sectionBodyColor

   @include useMinWidth(750px)
      &__desc
         width: 60%
         margin: 0 auto 2rem auto

      &
         padding: 7rem 0

   @include useMinWidth(1020px)
      &__desc
         width: 50%

   @include useMinWidth(1132px)
      &__desc
         width: 40%
sources.styles\\technology.sass:
.technology
   background: white
   padding: 5rem 0

   &__desc
      text-align: center

   &__header
      display: inline
      position: relative

      &::after
         content: ''
         background: $primaryBlue
         height: 2px
         display: block
         position: absolute
         width: 70%
         left: 50%
         transform: translate(-50%, 28px)

   &__body
      margin-top: 44px + 28px
      color: $sectionBodyColor

   @include useMinWidth(750px)
      &__desc
         // width: 60%
         margin: 0 auto 2rem auto

      &
         padding: 7rem 0

   // @include useMinWidth(1020px)
   //    &__desc
   //       width: 50%

   // @include useMinWidth(1132px)
   //    &__desc
   //       width: 40%
      
   $boxWidth: 162px * .8
   $boxHeight: 148px * .8
    
   .small-boxes
      display: grid
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, $boxWidth)
      justify-content: center
      grid-gap: 1rem
      margin-top: 4rem

      .small-box

         &__block
            width: $boxWidth
            height: $boxHeight
            border-radius: 25px
            background: #FFFFFF
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25)

            &__img
               width: 100px
               height: 100px
               transform: translate(-2.9rem, -3.1rem) scale(.3)

            @import ./sprites
      
         &__desc
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.83)
            font-size: 14px

sources.styles\\modal.sass:
$modalRadius: 12px

.modal
   display: none
   z-index: 100
   position: fixed
   overflow-y: scroll
   top: 0
   left: 0
   width: 100%
   height: 100%
   background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.51)

   .modal-container
      margin-right: .5rem
      margin-left: .5rem

   &__nav
      background: #3E35D1
      border-radius: $modalRadius $modalRadius 0 0
      h2 
         font-weight: 500
         font-size: 20px
         color: white
         padding: 1rem 0
         margin-left: 1rem

   &__body
      z-index: 100
      width: 90%
      margin: 1rem auto
      background: #FFFFFF
      border-radius: $modalRadius

   &__content
      z-index: 100
      > div 
         display: block

      img
         width: 60%
         min-height: 90%
         max-height: 400px
         z-index: 101
         grid-area: img
         margin: 0 auto
         display: block

      &__info
         display: flex
         flex-direction: column
         grid-area: body
         text-align: center

         p:nth-of-type(2)
            font-weight: 500

            i
               color: #696969
               font-weight: normal
               font-style: normal

         &__btn-wrp
            padding: 1rem 0 2rem 0
            justify-self: flex-end

         button
            cursor: pointer
            outline: none
            border: 1px solid $primaryBlue
            color: $primaryBlue
            text-transform: uppercase
            background: white
            padding: .5rem 2rem
            min-width: 8rem
            margin-top: .5rem

         .modal__btn--primary
            background: $primaryBlue
            color: white

   @include useMinWidth(750px)
      &
         top: 75px
         height: calc(100% - 75px)

         &__body
            width: 70%

         &__nav h2 
            margin-left: 3rem

         &__content 
            .modal-container
               display: grid
               grid-template-rows: 2fr .5fr
               grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr
               grid-template-areas: 'img body' 'img body'

            &__info
               text-align: left

               &__btn-wrp
                  margin-top: 4rem

         img
            display: inline

   @include useMinMaxWidth(500px, 750px)
      &
         img 
            width: 40%
            max-height: 200px
